Nigeria Urges Partners to Invest in Oil, Gas, BusinessDay Says

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-08-09T08:25:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-09/nigeria-urges-partners-to-invest-in-oil-gas-businessday-says.html
Nigeria ’s state-owned oil company
urged its joint venture partners to invest in oil and gas
projects and not wait for passage of a new petroleum law,
 BusinessDay  reported, citing the company’s group managing
director, Austen Oniwon.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
 ebalagbogbo@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 